* google omniauth setup: https://github.com/zquestz/omniauth-google-oauth2
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-configure-devise-and-omniauth-for-your-rails-application
* google login (devise)
* users (devise)
* file attachment (carrierwave)
* link to online image
* batch add photos from google+, facebook or instagram
* soundcloud integration
* comments (acts as commentable)
* auto-detect location by EXIF data
* everything is public-read. 
* Can edit one's own content with login
* admin can edit anything